personalInfo.splInterest: Throwing the baseball and football with my brother, cooking up feasts for game days when I'm in town
personalInfo.clubAffl: Nicklaus GC at LionsGate (Overland Park, Kansas)

tourBios.curYrHigh: Competed on Latinoamérica, having qualified with a T14 at Qualifying School in Sebring, Fla. In 12 starts, made six cuts and posted two top-25s. Best outing was a T14 at the Volvo Colombian Classic in September. Finished the season 98th on the Order of Merit...Played in one Web.com Tour event, his hometown Digital Ally Open in August. Shot 72-68 and missed the cut.

tourBios.otherCarHigh: Was a first-team selection on the American Athletic Conference All-Academic team in 2014.
tourBios.personal: Graduated from Blue Valley North High School in Overland Park, Kan., in 2010...Brother, Alex, is a member of the 2015-16 SMU golf team...Uncle Ed is a World War II veteran...If not a professional golfer, would be a senator or governor or possibly president...First-tee entrance song would be "The Star-Spangled Banner."...Biggest thrill in golf was being a member of the winning SMU American Athletic Conference Championship in 2014 and advancing to the NCAA Championship match-play quarterfinals...Biggest thrill outside of golf was throwing a complete-game shutout in the state baseball finals at age 13...Favorite sports teams are Philadelphia Eagles, Kansas City Royals, SMU and Villanova...Other favorites include LeBron James (non-golfer athletes), American Sniper and One Survivor (books), Kansas City and Bogota, Colombia (cities), Nicklaus GC at LionsGate and Cypress Point (golf courses), "One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest" and "Shutter Island" (movies) and "Homeland, "The League" and "Californication" (TV shows)...Most famous person met is George W. Bush...Motto is "I didn't come all this way to lay up."...Single best sporting event attended is game two of the 2015 Major League Baseball American League Championship Series between the Kansas City Royals and the Toronto Blue Jays...Dream foursome would be his parentsand brother Alex...Not many people know "I'm a good dancer."...Bucket-list item is winning the Masters...Twitter handle is hhiggs@SMU.
